      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats retain their original matte texture and factory scent, with absolutely no creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. This is a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
